WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: sq

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.709
Jemi mbledhur sot te gjithe ketu

00:00:17.334 --> 00:00:26.209
per ti kushtuar respektin tone Shri Ganeshes.

00:00:34.375 --> 00:00:39.250
Ganapatipule ka nje domethenie te vecante

00:00:45.875 --> 00:00:51.375
sepse Ai eshte Mahaganesha.

00:00:54.250 --> 00:00:57.375
Ganesha tek Mooladhara

00:00:58.792 --> 00:01:01.792
behet Mahaganesha

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.167
ne Virata, qe eshte truri.

00:01:08.417 --> 00:01:13.083
Kjo do te thote qe eshte vendi i Shri Ganesha.

00:01:14.626 --> 00:01:18.167
Qe do te thote se Shri Ganesha qeveris

00:01:19.292 --> 00:01:28.792
nga ky vend principin e pafajesise.

00:01:30.292 --> 00:01:35.417
Sic e dini mire eshte e vendosur prapa

00:01:41.042 --> 00:01:44.626
ne zonen e optic thalamus,

00:01:44.958 --> 00:01:49.167
lobi optik sic e quajne,

00:01:52.917 --> 00:02:03.751
dhe eshte dhenesi i pafajesise per syte tuaj.

00:02:10.501 --> 00:02:13.792
Kur Ai misheriohet si Krishti

00:02:14.083 --> 00:02:19.626
qe eshte ketu ne balle, tek Agnya

00:02:20.875 --> 00:02:24.125
Ai e tha shume qarte qe

00:02:24.125 --> 00:02:28.125
"Ju nuk duhet te keni sy tradhtare (kuroreshkeles)."

00:02:30.626 --> 00:02:33.375
Kjo eshte delikate per t'u thene,

00:02:34.250 --> 00:02:36.792
te cilen njerezit nuk e kuptojne

00:02:37.833 --> 00:02:41.542
cili eshte kuptimi i fjales "kuroreshkeles."

00:02:43.751 --> 00:02:48.375
"Kuroreshkeles" do te thote "papasterti" ne fjalen e pergjithme.

00:02:48.751 --> 00:02:54.833
Asnje papasterti ne sy "nuk duhet te keni"

00:02:55.626 --> 00:02:58.542
eshte shume e veshtire.

00:02:58.917 --> 00:03:02.250
Ne vend te thenies qe te merrni realizimin tuaj

00:03:02.250 --> 00:03:04.917
dhe pastroni Agnyan tuaj te mbrapme,
.,

00:03:05.792 --> 00:03:07.626
Ai e ka thene ne nje forme shume te shkurter,

00:03:07.917 --> 00:03:11.167
"Ju nuk duhet te keni sy tradhtare (kuroreshkeles)."

00:03:12.125 --> 00:03:16.709
Dhe njerezit menduan, eshte nje situate e pamundur

00:03:17.875 --> 00:03:20.542
Sepse Ai nuk u lejua te jetonte gjate;

00:03:20.542 --> 00:03:23.334
ne fakt jeta e Tij publike eshte e kufizuar

00:03:23.334 --> 00:03:25.584
ne vetem 3 vjet e gjysem.

00:03:29.292 --> 00:03:34.250
Pra cfaredo te kete thene Ai ka nje domethenie te madhe,

00:03:34.542 --> 00:03:38.375
qe syte tuaj s'duhet te jene kuroreshkeles.

00:03:39.292 --> 00:03:43.417
Aty ku ka pafajesi nuk ka tradheti:

00:03:44.917 --> 00:03:47.917
do te thote nuk ka papasterti.

00:03:48.709 --> 00:03:50.792
Per shembull, me syte tane

00:03:51.167 --> 00:03:58.917
shohim dicka dhe duam ta zoterojme ate.

00:03:59.917 --> 00:04:02.250
Fillojme te mendojme.

00:04:03.125 --> 00:04:05.751
Mendimi fillon

00:04:06.958 --> 00:04:09.751
si nje zinxhir, njeri pas tjetrit.

00:04:10.250 --> 00:04:22.417
Pastaj futemi ne rrjeten e mendimeve te tmerrshme,

00:04:24.042 --> 00:04:27.417
dhe me pas behemi skllever te ketyre mendimeve.

00:04:27.917 --> 00:04:30.042
Madje edhe njohuria jone,

00:04:30.042 --> 00:04:33.501
syte tane shkojne ndaj gjerave

00:04:36.542 --> 00:04:38.375
qe jane jane shume bruto

00:04:38.375 --> 00:04:40.792
dhe ju cojne ne renie.

00:04:46.125 --> 00:04:50.375
Sic ka thene Shri Krishna qe Pema e Ndergjegjesimit

00:04:52.042 --> 00:04:55.417
rritet koke poshte,

00:04:55.917 --> 00:05:01.958
qe rrenjet jane ne tru

00:05:02.417 --> 00:05:05.417
dhe deget rriten per poshte.

00:05:05.417 --> 00:05:07.792
Ata qe kane shkuar drejt materializmit

00:05:07.792 --> 00:05:09.917
jane rritur per poshte.

00:05:10.334 --> 00:05:14.709
Ata qe kane shkuar drejt Hyjnores

00:05:14.709 --> 00:05:17.875
jane rritur per lart, pertej rrenjeve.

00:05:19.375 --> 00:05:22.584
Rrenja kryesore, qe e quajne taproot,

00:05:22.833 --> 00:05:30.459
rrenja kryesore eshte pafajesia, eshte Shri Ganesha.

00:05:31.125 --> 00:05:36.125
Dhe Ai behet Mahaganesha ne Ganapatipule.

00:05:37.791 --> 00:05:42.042
Ai eshte i rrethuar ketu

00:05:42.875 --> 00:05:46.250
nga Principi i Babait, Principi i Guruse

00:05:49.542 --> 00:05:59.667
se detit, oqeanit - Oqeanit Indian.

00:06:05.459 --> 00:06:12.584
Kjo eshte, ketu Ai behet nje Guru.

00:06:15.375 --> 00:06:17.542
Kur nje Sahaja yogi

00:06:18.417 --> 00:06:21.042
stabilizon Principin e tij te Shri Ganeshas,

00:06:21.042 --> 00:06:23.250
ai eshte ende nje femije.

00:06:27.334 --> 00:06:33.459
Sigurisht syte e tij fillojne te behen gjithnje e me te paster,

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:37.709
te fuqishem dhe te shndritshem.

00:06:39.417 --> 00:06:43.958
Duhet ta keni pare qe kur kundalini ju jep

00:06:45.292 --> 00:06:47.209
realizimin

00:06:47.501 --> 00:06:53.875
me pas syte tuaj fillojne te shndrisin,

00:06:54.375 --> 00:06:56.709
sikur ka nje shkendije ne sy,

00:06:56.917 --> 00:06:59.709
mund te krijoni nje shkendije.

00:07:01.667 --> 00:07:04.334
Me ego ajo mbulohet,

00:07:09.083 --> 00:07:17.875
me ego verbohet.

00:07:19.209 --> 00:07:24.709
Me superego mbulohet nga lotet.

00:07:27.917 --> 00:07:30.375
Por me pas kur qartesohen

00:07:30.875 --> 00:07:34.792
ju shikoni bukurine e syve,

00:07:40.250 --> 00:07:45.375
Shri Ganesha shkelqen nepermjet shikimeve tuaja.

00:07:53.375 --> 00:07:56.667
Tani vemendja fillon te rrjedhe

00:07:56.917 --> 00:08:00.292
prej dritares se tempullit te Shri Ganeshas.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:06.667
Por kur ju maturoheni,

00:08:10.542 --> 00:08:14.083
beheni Mahaganesha.

00:08:15.542 --> 00:08:18.459
Me pas Mahaganesha stabilizohet tek ju

00:08:18.958 --> 00:08:22.709
dhe ju beheni nje satguru,

00:08:23.667 --> 00:08:28.209
beheni nje guru hyjnor, mund t'i mesoni te tjeret.

00:08:30.917 --> 00:08:33.709
Edhe nje femije mund te jete i tille,

00:08:34.417 --> 00:08:37.792
por edhe nje person i rritur mund te jete budalla.

00:08:38.292 --> 00:08:46.584
Nuk ka lidhje me moshen, ngjyren, besimin (kredon) apo kasten,

00:08:47.083 --> 00:08:52.751
Eshte nje gjendje te cilen dikush mund ta arrije ne cdo kohe.

00:08:53.125 --> 00:08:56.250
Sic mund te themi ketu patem Gyaneshwara,

00:08:56.501 --> 00:08:58.751
qe ne nje moshe shume te re

00:09:02.833 --> 00:09:07.542
kompozoi te madhen Gyaneshwari.

00:09:09.751 --> 00:09:11.209
Sic e keni pare dje,

00:09:11.501 --> 00:09:14.167
ne moshen dymbedhjete vjecare Gorakhnath

00:09:15.125 --> 00:09:18.792
stabilizoi Mahaganeshan e tij.

00:09:23.833 --> 00:09:28.042
Por nese nuk provoni te ngjiteni,

00:09:28.042 --> 00:09:30.250
atehere do mbeteni ne te njejten faze

00:09:30.250 --> 00:09:32.375
edhe kur te plakeni.

00:09:33.626 --> 00:09:37.417
Pra maturia eshte treguesi.

00:09:38.167 --> 00:09:41.292
Ketu, sic shihni ne Ganapatipule,

00:09:41.626 --> 00:09:47.709
Shri Ganesha eshte ne formen e saj te plote, te maturuar

00:09:52.125 --> 00:09:56.709
keshtu qe ne zhvillojme gjithashtu Mahaganeshan tone

00:09:56.709 --> 00:09:58.375
brenda vetes sone,

00:09:59.292 --> 00:10:09.292
dhe syte tane behen te paster, te fuqishem dhe hyjnore.

00:10:16.792 --> 00:10:19.417
Me punen e duhur,

00:10:21.250 --> 00:10:30.125
jam e sigurte qe ne mund te stabilizojme ate faze brenda vetes sone.

00:10:33.875 --> 00:10:39.209
Sot kemi ardhur ne Ganapatipule, ka nje domethenie te madhe,

00:10:39.791 --> 00:10:41.334
midis Asthavinayaka(tete Swayambhus te Shri Ganesha),

00:10:41.875 --> 00:10:44.833
Eshte vendi i Mahaganeshas.

00:10:46.875 --> 00:10:52.375
Mahaganesha eshte Pithadhish (Qeverises i te gjitha pitave)

00:10:54.751 --> 00:10:56.792
dhe duke u ulur ne kete pita,

00:11:00.042 --> 00:11:02.958
ai mbron gjithe Ganesha Swayambhus.

00:11:05.167 --> 00:11:07.667
Ai ka njohurine e te gjithe Omakara-ve,

00:11:09.292 --> 00:11:13.791
pasi ai ka arritur Guru Tatwa (Principin e Guruse ).

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:19.501
Nese shohim rreth e rrotull,

00:11:20.417 --> 00:11:22.501
oqeani, kaq i bukur dhe i paster

00:11:23.375 --> 00:11:26.042
eshte duke lare kembet e ketij Ganapati,

00:11:27.542 --> 00:11:36.209
sepse oqeani perfaqeson Guru Tatwa,

00:11:37.375 --> 00:11:42.542
dhe me kete Guru Tatwa, ai lan kembet e   Shri Ganeshas

00:11:45.791 --> 00:11:49.584
keshtu duhet te ndodhe me te gjithe Sahaja Yogis.

00:11:50.958 --> 00:11:53.751
Kur Ganesha Stuthi kryhet me pas Shri Ganesha eshte stabilizuar

00:11:54.501 --> 00:11:58.375
dhe pastaj me Mahalakshmi Tatwa

00:12:01.791 --> 00:12:04.209
ju duhet te beheni Mahaganeshas.

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:10.667
Kjo faze mund te arrihet nga femije te vegjel dhe te medhenj,

00:12:11.584 --> 00:12:15.501
njerez te moshuar, gra dhe  cdokush,

00:12:16.334 --> 00:12:22.917
nese ata mund te mbajne sjelljen e drejteperdrejte,

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:28.833
te cilen e quajme si  Saralya  ne Marathi, ose sic thone  Abhodita

00:12:29.459 --> 00:12:35.250
ose pafajesine, kur eshte e pervetesuar njehere tek ne,

00:12:36.626 --> 00:12:38.751
ne mund te arrijme Principin e Guruse.

00:12:39.167 --> 00:12:44.083
Cilido Guru, qe nuk ka kete natyre te drejteperdrejte

00:12:44.209 --> 00:12:46.958
dhe te pafajeshme, nuk mund te jete kurre nje Guru,

00:12:47.167 --> 00:12:48.292
ai eshte nje Aguru (Guru i rreme).

00:12:48.792 --> 00:12:52.751
Personi, vemendja e te cilit eshte gjithmone ne Fuqine Hyjnore,

00:12:53.751 --> 00:12:55.751
vetem ai behet nje Guru i vertete.

00:12:59.417 --> 00:13:02.751
Vemendja e qenieve normale njerezore eshte zvetenuar,

00:13:03.792 --> 00:13:07.958
s'eshte e paster. Prandaj Krishti ka thene,

00:13:08.417 --> 00:13:12.125
qe s'duhet te kete tradheti (kuroreshkelje) ne syte tuaj,

00:13:12.667 --> 00:13:17.375
do te thote qe nese e con vemendjen ne dicka,

00:13:18.042 --> 00:13:22.000
ne fillojme te mendojme shume e ide te cuditshme vijne ne mendjen tone,

00:13:22.375 --> 00:13:24.000
se si mund ta fitoj kete gje

00:13:24.250 --> 00:13:25.751
dhe pse mos ta marr kete gje,

00:13:25.958 --> 00:13:27.375
dhe mendime te tjera si "pse?" dhe "pse jo?"

00:13:27.958 --> 00:13:30.501
Nese ne shohim dicka dhe fillojme te mendojme, atehere

00:13:31.083 --> 00:13:35.250
nuk e kemi kaluar akoma Cakran Agnya.

00:13:36.791 --> 00:13:38.626
Cfaredo objekti te shihni, duhet te beheni pamendime,

00:13:38.791 --> 00:13:44.833
sidomos ne vendbanimin e pasurise dhe prosperitetit

00:13:45.042 --> 00:13:49.833
aty ka Perendi dhe Perendesha te shumte

00:13:50.083 --> 00:13:52.250
te pakten duke pare ata, njeriu duhet te behet pamendime.

00:13:52.292 --> 00:13:53.709
Pasi te kemi arritur gjendjen e vetedijes pamenduar,

00:13:54.042 --> 00:13:55.958
nuk do te mbetet me asnje perversitet (zvetenim) ne vemendjen tone.

00:13:56.083 --> 00:13:58.542
Mendimet qe zvetenojne mendjen nuk do te vijne me,

00:13:59.125 --> 00:14:00.791
pra si do ndikoje mbi ju perversiteti?

00:14:03.042 --> 00:14:04.667
Nenkupton ate qe tha Krishti,

00:14:04.751 --> 00:14:07.334
nuk duhet te keni sy kuroreshkeles.

00:14:07.709 --> 00:14:10.875
Ata duhen te jene aq te paster, si rrezet e diellit,

00:14:11.250 --> 00:14:16.667
kur bien mbi peme, nuk e thithin pisllekun,

00:14:17.417 --> 00:14:22.042
ato ushqehen dhe i ushqejne ato, jo vetem kaq

00:14:22.459 --> 00:14:24.792
por u japin atyre edhe force.

00:14:25.501 --> 00:14:28.042
Ne te njejten menyre,

00:14:28.334 --> 00:14:32.334
Sahaja Yogis duhet te kene shkelqim te tille ne syte e tyre, qe

00:14:32.542 --> 00:14:40.917
te mund te krijojne nje atmosfere shume te paster ne gjithe boten.

00:14:41.542 --> 00:14:45.709
Pastertia ne atmosfere eshte ajo qe duhet sot, kudo.

00:14:46.709 --> 00:14:55.250
ne menyre qe paqja, gezimi dhe fuqia hyjnore te zoteroje ne kete bote.

00:14:58.875 --> 00:15:02.792
Vetem duke i thurur lavde Shri Ganeshes mund te mos jete mjaftueshem,

00:15:03.000 --> 00:15:05.000
nevojitet qe Shri Ganesha te jete zgjuar brenda nesh

00:15:05.542 --> 00:15:07.875
dhe ai duhet te zhvillohet ne fazen e Mahaganeshas.

00:15:08.459 --> 00:15:10.709
Vetem pasi te kemi arritur fazen e Mahaganeshas,

00:15:10.792 --> 00:15:14.626
mund te perfitoje vendi yne dhe gjithashtu permes vendit tone,

00:15:14.791 --> 00:15:16.792
vendet e tjera mund te perfitojne nga kjo faze.

00:15:16.917 --> 00:15:19.125
Ne do te drejtojme te tjeret,

00:15:19.209 --> 00:15:24.542
por nese nuk do e marrim kete pergjegjesi,

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:28.709
atehere s'e them dot se cfare do te ndodhe ne kete bote.

00:15:29.167 --> 00:15:32.000
Kam nje kerkese ndaj te gjitheve ju,

00:15:32.250 --> 00:15:35.083
te heqim gjithe tradhetine nga syte tane.

00:15:35.292 --> 00:15:40.501
Per kete ne kemi mantran e Nirvichara ne  Sahaja Yoga.

00:15:40.917 --> 00:15:42.501
Mos lejoni mendimet t'ju dominojne,

00:15:42.584 --> 00:15:44.542
nese vijne mendimet, atehere thoni

00:15:45.042 --> 00:15:49.167
 Yen Neti Neti Vachane  (nuk ekziston)

00:15:49.667 --> 00:15:52.209
ose themi   Kshama Keli, Kshama Keli   (Une fal, une fal),

00:15:52.667 --> 00:15:54.125
keshtu ky mendim eshte shkaterruar

00:15:54.209 --> 00:15:55.875
dhe kur shkujdesja eshte arritur,

00:15:57.417 --> 00:16:01.626
atehere perversiteti i mendjes ndalon.

00:16:01.833 --> 00:16:04.292
Cdo kush duhet te beje nje perpjekje,

00:16:04.501 --> 00:16:07.042
qe syte tuaj mos te jene tradhtare (kuroreshkeles).

00:16:07.292 --> 00:16:09.791
 "Nese ka perversitet ne mendjen time per shkak te syve,

00:16:09.917 --> 00:16:14.125
atehere nuk dua te kem sy te tille", tha Shenjti Tukaram,

00:16:14.375 --> 00:16:17.459
 "atehere, eshte me mire te jesh i verber".

00:16:17.709 --> 00:16:22.958
Nga nje ane, eshte me mire te jesh i verber,

00:16:23.042 --> 00:16:25.000
se te kesh perversitet ne mendje.

00:16:25.125 --> 00:16:27.626
Me mire te kesh sy te brendshem te shohesh Hyjnoren.

00:16:27.667 --> 00:16:29.958
Kur keto dy principe bashkohen si duhet,

00:16:30.501 --> 00:16:33.334
atehere mund te themi se

00:16:33.584 --> 00:16:35.751
Sahaja Yogi ka arritur Principin e Guruse.

00:16:36.667 --> 00:16:42.167
Ju bekoje te gjitheve, qe ketu ne Ganapatipule,

00:16:42.417 --> 00:16:46.667
vendin e  Mahaganeshas, me hirin e tij te vecante,

00:16:47.083 --> 00:16:50.250
te gjithe mund te arrini Principin e Guruse sa me shpejt te jete e mundur.

